Weird day. Still havent had much sleep, and I feel pretty ill. Probably just the amount of pepsi max I drink, but I still feel ill right now. I have a habit of doing stupid things like that x3 Grandad might have the starts of the bug that is going around, hope im not sharing that. I wonder if when I get the antidepressants it'll make my stomach even worse..
Blargh. Just blargh.
Cant wait to have this day over and done with, feel so ill at-ease. --;

A RDKF skin-rendition of the very first decent drawing I ever did in my life. The Ensutak was a cheesy-ass alien race I invented right at the start of secondary school. The skin -nearly- got scrapped, but I put in an extra hour, and it actually turned out pretty damn cool. It'll look weird in action, but hopefully with some comedic voicefile for its combat stuffs, it'd rule ^^;

